<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334580>
    bibo:endPage "130" ;
    bibo:journal "Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2012-12-17" ;
    bibo:startPage "107" ;
    bibo:volume "52" ;
    dc:creator "Fikáček, Martin; Delgado, Juan A.; Gentili, Elio" ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "The Hydrophiloid beetles of Socotra Island (Coleoptera: Georissidae, Hydrophilidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334586>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334588>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334592> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334586>
    dc:description "Figs. 7–8. Genitalia of Socotran endemic Georissus species. 7 – G. maritimus sp. nov. (a, b: two different ventral views of the same aedeagus; c: lateral view); 8 – G. nemo sp. nov., ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5334586/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334588>
    dc:description "Figs. 9–14. Georissus nemo sp. nov. (9–13 – paratype; 14 – holotype). 9 – pronotum and elytra in dorsal view; 10 – head, dorsal view; 11–12 – detail of pronotum (11 – dorsal view; 12 – dorsolateral view); 13 – elytron, dorsolateral view; 14 – abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5334588/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5334592>
    dc:description "Figs. 15–22.Socotran endemic Georissus species and their habitats. 15–16 – G. maritimus sp. nov.(15 – dorsal view; 16 – lateral view). 17–18 – G. nemo sp. nov. (17 – dorsal view; 18 – lateral view). 19–20 – the sand tongue 3 km NE of Shuab, type locality of G. maritimus sp. nov. (19 – general view of the habitat; 20 – satellite view showing the position of the locality); 21–22 – the stream at Arhar, type locality of G. nemo sp. nov. (21 – general view of the habitat; 22 – satellite view showing the position of the locality)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5334592/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

